creator: Mobile Solutions Worldwide
descriptionHtml:
Application scans your device for presence of vulnerabilities.

You can scan
• Background processes
• Installed apps
• Files from SD card

Features
• Stop or uninstall applications based on the scan result.
• Notification manager to disable apps with push notifications
• Task manager to stop background apps which drain battery
• App Manager to manage the installed apps
• Support Android 9
• Support Smart TV
• Speed up scanning with machine learning
descriptionShort: Application scans your device for presence of vulnerabilities.
